trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRoleCollection" /> class is a read-only collection that contains <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRoleCollection" /> é uma coleção somente leitura que contém objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object to search for in this collection.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> a ser pesquisado nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: Determines if the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object is in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> especificado está nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object is in this collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> estiver nesta coleção; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="role" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="role" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> objects that receives the elements of this collection.
trans-unit.target: A matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> que recebe os elementos desta coleção.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>roles</c> where this method starts copying this collection.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero em <c>funções</c> em que esse método começa a copiar essa coleção.

trans-unit.source: Copies all <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> objects in this collection to the specified array, starting at the specified index in the array.
trans-unit.target: Copia todos os objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> nesta coleção para a matriz especificada, iniciando no índice especificado na matriz.

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: Uma chamada ao serviço do diretório subjacente resultou em um erro.

trans-unit.source: The destination array is not large enough to hold the required number of elements.
trans-unit.target: A matriz de destino não é grande o suficiente para manter o número necessário de elementos.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="roles" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="roles" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> specified is out of range of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: O <paramref name="index" /> especificado está fora do intervalo da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object to search for in this collection.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> a ser pesquisado nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns the index of the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o índice da primeira ocorrência do objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> especificado nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the first matching object.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero do primeiro objeto de correspondência.

trans-unit.source: Returns -1 if no member of this collection is identical to the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Retornará -1 se nenhum membro dessa coleção for idêntico ao objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" />.

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: Uma chamada ao serviço do diretório subjacente resultou em um erro.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="role" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="role" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object to get.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero do objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> a ser obtido.

trans-unit.source: Gets an <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> object that exists at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectoryRole" /> objeto que existe no índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> specified is out of range of the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <paramref name="index" /> especificado está fora do intervalo da coleção.
